{"type":"message","id":"d019e8a1","parentId":"76a14777","timestamp":"2026-03-24T22:41:55.430Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Office join失败了，提示\"请提供接入密钥\"。可能是join key不对。让我先不管这个，继续执行核心任务：spawn工部开发前端。\n\n根据任务要求，我需要：\n1. 检查后端API文档\n2. 准备工部开发任务详情\n3. Spawn工部agent\n4. 提供session key和runId作为证据\n\n让我先检查项目结构，了解后端API的情况。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b9533872ed71457d9cf39bf2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find /root/.openclaw/tang-sansheng -type f -name \"*.cs\" -o -name \"*.csproj\" | grep -E \"(Program|Startup|Controller|Account)\" | head -20"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":1078,"output":149,"cacheRead":17344,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18571,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774392111201}}
{"type":"message","id":"36865be1","parentId":"d019e8a1","timestamp":"2026-03-24T22:41:55.746Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_b9533872ed71457d9cf39bf2","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/root/.openclaw/tang-sansheng/projects/tianyou-platform/backend/src/Tianyou.Api/Controllers/AuthController.cs\n/root/.openclaw/tang-sansheng/projects/tianyou-platform/backend/src/Tianyou.Api/Program.cs"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":301,"aggregated":"/root/.openclaw/tang-sansheng/projects/tianyou-platform/backend/src/Tianyou.Api/Controllers/AuthController.cs\n/root/.openclaw/tang-sansheng/projects/tianyou-platform/backend/src/Tianyou.Api/Program.cs","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/tang-sansheng/workspace-zhongshu"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774392115738}}
{"type":"message","id":"42c265e3","parentId":"36865be1","timestamp":"2026-03-24T22:41:58.599Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，找到了后端项目。让我检查AuthController和Program.cs，了解API接口的详细信息。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c05ac1877761428c86c98831","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/tang-sansheng/projects/tianyou-platform/backend/src/Tianyou.Api/Controllers/AuthController.cs"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d0c3722dd1a34b28a9846368","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/tang-sansheng/projects/tianyou-platform/backend/src/Tianyou.Api/Program.cs"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":258,"output":89,"cacheRead":18368,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18715,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774392115747}}
{"type":"message","id":"f29f3684","parentId":"42c265e3","timestamp":"2026-03-24T22:41:58.648Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_c05ac1877761428c86c98831","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Authorization;\nusing Microsoft.AspNetCore.Mvc;\nusing System.Security.Claims;\nusing Tianyou.Application.Services;\n\nnamespace Tianyou.Api.Controllers;\n\n/// <summary>\n/// 认证控制器\n/// </summary>\n[ApiController]\n[Route(\"api/auth\")]\npublic class AuthController : ControllerBase\n{\n    private readonly AuthService _authService;\n    private readonly ILogger<AuthController> _logger;\n    \n    public AuthController(AuthService authService, ILogger<AuthController> logger)\n    {\n        _authService = authService;\n        _logger = logger;\n    }\n    \n    /// <summary>\n    /// 用户注册\n    /// </summary>\n    [HttpPost(\"register\")]\n    [ProducesResponseType(StatusCodes.Status200OK)]\n    [ProducesResponseType(StatusCodes.Status400BadRequest)]\n    public async Task<IActionResult> Register([FromBody] RegisterRequest request)\n    {\n        try\n        {\n            var (user, token) = await _authService.RegisterAsync(\n                request.Username,\n                request.Email,\n                request.Password,\n                request.FullName);\n            \n            _logger.LogInformation(\"用户注册成功: {Username}\", request.Username);\n            \n            return Ok(new\n            {\n                success = true,\n                data = new\n                {\n                    userId = user.Id,\n                    username = user.Username,\n                    email = user.Email,\n                    fullName = user.FullName,\n                    token,\n                    expiresIn = 86400 // 24小时\n                }\n            });\n        }\n        catch (Exception ex)\n        {\n            _logger.LogWarning(ex, \"用户注册失败: {Username}\", request.Username);\n            return BadRequest(new { success = false, message = ex.Message });\n        }\n    }\n    \n    /// <summary>\n    /// 用户登录\n    /// </summary>\n    [HttpPost(\"login\")]\n    [ProducesResponseType(StatusCodes.Status200OK)]\n    [ProducesResponseType(StatusCodes.Status401Unauthorized)]\n    public async Task<IActionResult> Login([FromBody] LoginRequest request)\n    {\n        try\n        {\n            var (user, token) = await _authService.LoginAsync(request.Username, request.Password);\n            \n            _logger.LogInformation(\"用户登录成功: {Username}\", request.Username);\n            \n            return Ok(new\n            {\n                success = true,\n                data = new\n                {\n                    userId = user.Id,\n                    username = user.Username,\n                    email = user.Email,\n                    fullName = user.FullName,\n                    token,\n                    expiresIn = 86400\n                }\n            });\n        }\n        catch (Exception ex)\n        {\n            _logger.LogWarning(ex, \"用户登录失败: {Username}\", request.Username);\n            return Unauthorized(new { success = false, message = ex.Message });\n        }\n    }\n    \n    /// <summary>\n    /// 获取当前用户信息\n    /// </summary>\n    [Authorize]\n    [HttpGet(\"me\")]\n    [ProducesResponseType(StatusCodes.Status200OK)]\n    [ProducesResponseType(StatusCodes.Status401Unauthorized)]\n    public async Task<IActionResult> GetCurrentUser()\n    {\n        var userIdClaim = User.FindFirst(ClaimTypes.NameIdentifier)?.Value;\n        \n        if (string.IsNullOrEmpty(userIdClaim))\n        {\n            return Unauthorized(new { success = false, message = \"无效的Token\" });\n        }\n        \n        var username = User.FindFirst(ClaimTypes.Name)?.Value;\n        var email = User.FindFirst(ClaimTypes.Email)?.Value;\n        var fullName = User.FindFirst(\"fullName\")?.Value;\n        var roles = User.FindAll(ClaimTypes.Role).Select(c => c.Value).ToList();\n        var permissions = User.FindAll(\"permission\").Select(c => c.Value).ToList();\n        \n        return Ok(new\n        {\n            success = true,\n            data = new\n            {\n                userId = userIdClaim,\n                username,\n                email,\n                fullName,\n                roles,\n                permissions\n            }\n        });\n    }\n    \n    /// <summary>\n    /// 修改密码\n    /// </summary>\n    [Authorize]\n    [HttpPut(\"password\")]\n    [ProducesResponseType(StatusCodes.Status200OK)]\n    [ProducesResponseType(StatusCodes.Status400BadRequest)]\n    [ProducesResponseType(StatusCodes.Status401Unauthorized)]\n    public async Task<IActionResult> ChangePassword([FromBody] ChangePasswordRequest request)\n    {\n        var userIdClaim = User.FindFirst(ClaimTypes.NameIdentifier)?.Value;\n        \n        if (string.IsNullOrEmpty(userIdClaim))\n        {\n            return Unauthorized(new { success = false, message = \"无效的Token\" });\n        }\n        \n        // TODO: 实现修改密码逻辑\n        \n        return Ok(new { success = true, message = \"密码修改成功\" });\n    }\n}\n\n// DTO类\npublic record RegisterRequest(string Username, string Email, string Password, string FullName);\npublic record LoginRequest(string Username, string Password);\npublic record ChangePasswordRequest(string OldPassword, string NewPassword);"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774392118638}}
{"type":"message","id":"b0991f53","parentId":"f29f3684","timestamp":"2026-03-24T22:41:58.657Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_d0c3722dd1a34b28a9846368","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Authentication.JwtBearer;\nusing Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore;\nusing Microsoft.IdentityModel.Tokens;\nusing Microsoft.OpenApi.Models;\nusing System.Text;\nusing Tianyou.Application.Services;\nusing Tianyou.Infrastructure.Data;\n\nvar builder = WebApplication.CreateBuilder(args);\n\n// 添加数据库上下文（SQLite）\nbuilder.Services.AddDbContext<TianyouDbContext>(options =>\n    options.UseSqlite(builder.Configuration.GetConnectionString(\"DefaultConnection\")));\n\n// 添加服务\nbuilder.Services.AddScoped<AuthService>();\n\n// 配置JWT认证\nvar jwtSettings = builder.Configuration.GetSection(\"Jwt\");\nvar key = Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(jwtSettings[\"Key\"]!);\n\nbuilder.Services.AddAuthentication(options =>\n{\n    options.DefaultAuthenticateScheme = JwtBearerDefaults.AuthenticationScheme;\n    options.DefaultChallengeScheme = JwtBearerDefaults.AuthenticationScheme;\n})\n.AddJwtBearer(options =>\n{\n    options.TokenValidationParameters = new TokenValidationParameters\n    {\n        ValidateIssuer = true,\n        ValidateAudience = true,\n        ValidateLifetime = true,\n        ValidateIssuerSigningKey = true,\n        ValidIssuer = jwtSettings[\"Issuer\"],\n        ValidAudience = jwtSettings[\"Audience\"],\n        IssuerSigningKey = new SymmetricSecurityKey(key),\n        ClockSkew = TimeSpan.Zero\n    };\n});\n\nbuilder.Services.AddAuthorization();\nbuilder.Services.AddControllers();\nbuilder.Services.AddEndpointsApiExplorer();\n\n// 配置Swagger\nbuilder.Services.AddSwaggerGen(c =>\n{\n    c.SwaggerDoc(\"v1\", new OpenApiInfo\n    {\n        Title = \"Tianyou API\",\n        Version = \"v1\",\n        Description = \"Tianyou低代码平台API\",\n        Contact = new OpenApiContact\n        {\n            Name = \"Tianyou Team\",\n            Email = \"support@tianyou.com\"\n        }\n    });\n    \n    // 添加JWT认证\n    c.AddSecurityDefinition(\"Bearer\", new OpenApiSecurityScheme\n    {\n        Description = \"JWT Authorization header using the Bearer scheme.\",\n        Name = \"Authorization\",\n        In = ParameterLocation.Header,\n        Type = SecuritySchemeType.ApiKey,\n        Scheme = \"Bearer\"\n    });\n    \n    c.AddSecurityRequirement(new OpenApiSecurityRequirement\n    {\n        {\n            new OpenApiSecurityScheme\n            {\n                Reference = new OpenApiReference\n                {\n                    Type = ReferenceType.SecurityScheme,\n                    Id = \"Bearer\"\n                }\n            },\n            Array.Empty<string>()\n        }\n    });\n});\n\n// 配置CORS\nbuilder.Services.AddCors(options =>\n{\n    options.AddPolicy(\"AllowAll\", policy =>\n    {\n        policy.AllowAnyOrigin()\n              .AllowAnyMethod()\n              .AllowAnyHeader();\n    });\n});\n\nvar app = builder.Build();\n\n// 自动运行数据库迁移和种子数据\nusing (var scope = app.Services.CreateScope())\n{\n    var context = scope.ServiceProvider.GetRequiredService<TianyouDbContext>();\n    context.Database.EnsureCreated();\n    Console.WriteLine(\"✅ SQLite数据库已创建\");\n}\n\n// 开发环境启用Swagger\nif (app.Environment.IsDevelopment())\n{\n    app.UseSwagger();\n    app.UseSwaggerUI(c =>\n    {\n        c.SwaggerEndpoint(\"/swagger/v1/swagger.json\", \"Tianyou API v1\");\n        c.RoutePrefix = \"swagger\";\n    });\n}\n\napp.UseHttpsRedirection();\napp.UseCors(\"AllowAll\");\napp.UseAuthentication();\napp.UseAuthorization();\napp.MapControllers();\n\n// 健康检查\napp.MapGet(\"/health\", () => Results.Ok(\"Healthy\"));\napp.MapGet(\"/\", () => Results.Ok(\"Tianyou API is running!\"));\n\napp.Run();"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774392118650}}
{"type":"message","id":"1722af8b","parentId":"b0991f53","timestamp":"2026-03-24T22:42:04.463Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"很好！我已经了解了后端API的详细信息：\n\n**API接口**：\n1. POST /api/auth/register - 用户注册\n   - 参数：Username, Email, Password, FullName\n   - 返回：userId, username, email, fullName, token, expiresIn\n\n2. POST /api/auth/login - 用户登录\n   - 参数：Username, Password\n   - 返回：userId, username, email, fullName, token, expiresIn\n\n3. GET /api/auth/me - 获取当前用户信息（需要JWT认证）\n   - Header: Authorization: Bearer {token}\n   - 返回：userId, username, email, fullName, roles, permissions\n\n4. PUT /api/auth/password - 修改密码（需要JWT认证）\n\n**技术栈**：\n- 后端：ASP.NET Core + SQLite + JWT认证\n- CORS：已配置AllowAll\n- API地址：http://localhost:5000\n\n现在我需要检查是否已经有前端项目，然后spawn工部agent来开发Blazor WebAssembly前端。\n\n让我先检查项目结构：","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_db9d1d017e484c26af451e2c","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la /root/.openclaw/tang-sansheng/projects/tianyou-platform/"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":1771,"output":247,"cacheRead":18624,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20642,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774392118658}}
